channel.title: Can't Login?
channel.description: Hey everyone I just re-compiled my server, and I got on, then it dc'd me. Now, whenever I try and log on, it either doesn't let me on, or nulls me, or says 'Your account is already logged in...Try again in 60 seconds.' I have tried using 'voule' (auto-restart) and re-compiling. Help please someone!
